,Recommended,258010,31238665,Posted: 19 April,all,YANDY INC,"This game went under the radar for the most part. If any indie game deserves the title of hidden gem it is this one. There are already a lot of reviews that go in depth with the features and aspects of this game so for this one I am going to forgo my usual analysis.I just wanted the opprotunity to let any prospective buyers to know that this game is worth far in excess of the asking price. YOU WILL get your enjoyment out of this game if you enjoy any of what this mash up of genre's have to offer.I would also suggest that if you are looking for a more free roaming experience do NOT give up on this game at first. The beginning missions are linear but that is mostly to get you aquainted with the many different great features this game has to offer. It has many to offer.For a team of two brothers this is one of the best indie projects I have experienced on steam out of just under 1200 indie games I have in my library and families libraries. I would put this in terms of solid sheer quality above a much more expensive game like The Witness. You are going to get a HECK of a lot more bang for your buck value to price wise here then you will in most other indie games on this storefront.If you are not the biggest fan of sci fi, space sim, there is a lot here for you in the plucky and well written dialogue and twin stick shooter action.If you are not the biggest fan of shallow end action without depth, there is a LOT here for you in the depths of the rpg mechanics and role building.It takes the best of both worlds and wraps it into one of the best indie packages of the last 5 years. You may not be wowwed by state of the art graphics or a bazillion hours of gameplay content. But they really put their heart in soul into this one and it shows across the board. There is far more then a satisfying amount of content here. The opening stages alone if you are not a mega fast speed runner may take you 10+ hours alone. That is before it opens up beautifully.Please if you are reticent to take risks on games, this is one you wont be sorry for pulling the trigger on. I would happily stake any small reputation I have on it.Have a great day and game on brutha."
